OL,3,CWalk-in mental health facility opens
OL,4,Cin area with high suicide rate
OL,6,FA new walk-in mental health and
OL,7,Fwellbeing hub has officially opened in
OL,8,FCumbria to tackle poor mental health.
OL,10,FHope Haven in Whitehaven is one of six
OL,11,Fcentres across England which are part
OL,12,Fof an NHS trial to give people the
OL,13,Fsupport they need at the earliest
OL,14,Fstage, before people reache crisis
OL,15,Fpoint.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
