OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1774455106
OL,3,CWalk-in mental health facility opens
OL,4,Cin area with high suicide rate
OL,6,FThe Cumberland Council local authority
OL,7,Farea has the third highest rate of
OL,8,Fsuicide in England, at 19.4 suicides
OL,9,Fper 100,000 people - compared to the
OL,10,FEngland-wide average of 10.9 per
OL,11,F100,000.
OL,13,FThis represents a significant increase
OL,14,Ffrom 2017-19, when the suicide rate in
OL,15,FCumberland was 13.1 per 100,000.
OL,17,FThe Hope Haven hub offers support with
OL,18,Feverything from physical and mental
OL,19,Fhealth to drug or alcohol addiction,
OL,20,Ffrom work or housing advice to help
OL,21,Fwith budgeting.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
