OL,3,CWalk-in mental health facility opens
OL,4,Cin area with high suicide rate
OL,6,FSituated on King Street and open until
OL,7,Fmidnight seven days a week, it
OL,8,Fdelivers this help without the need
OL,9,Ffor referrals or joining waiting lists.
OL,11,FThe service is a partnership between
OL,12,Fthe Cumbria, Northumberland, Tyne and
OL,13,FWear NHS Foundation Trust (CNTW), the
OL,14,FWhitehaven Community Trust, and
OL,15,Fvarious other local health bodies.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
