OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1774455106
OL,3,CWalk-in mental health facility opens
OL,4,Cin area with high suicide rate
OL,6,FDavid Storm, Associate Director for
OL,7,FAccess and Community Services at CNTW
OL,8,Fsaid: "What makes Hope Haven unique is
OL,9,Fthat if you need more than one type of
OL,10,Fsupport, we'll build that around you `
OL,11,Frather than people getting passed
OL,12,Fbetween different services."
OL,14,FOver 150 people have already been
OL,15,Fprovided with these services since
OL,16,FDecember, at a temporary home at
OL,17,FWhitehaven's Senhouse Centre.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
