CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1774455106
OL,3,CWalk-in mental health facility opens
OL,4,Cin area with high suicide rate
OL,6,FMr Storm continued: "We have already
OL,7,Fseen the impact we can have providing
OL,8,Flocal people with this type of
OL,9,Fsupport, and our move to King Street
OL,10,Fwill increase what we are able to
OL,11,Foffer to people across Copeland.
OL,13,F"So come and talk to us. You'll get a
OL,14,Fwarm welcome from one of our team, and
OL,15,Fthey'll listen to you to find out how
OL,16,Fwe can help."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
